The paper deals with the construction of linear codes and the determination of their weight distributions, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of simplicial complexes suggests that the paper may also be relevant to computational geometry (cs.CG) and algebraic topology (cs.GT). Finally, the study of optimal codes is related to coding theory (cs.CC).
